title: Adopt Me Clone
description: A fully functional Adopt Me clone with all the features of the original game. Includes pet system, housing, and trading.

faq.question: Is this the full game?
faq.answer: Yes, this includes all features from the original Adopt Me game.

faq.question: Can I monetize this?
faq.answer: Yes, you can add your own monetization to this game.
